# Resend API Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://resend.com/api-keys

# REQUIRED: Your Resend API key
RESEND_API_KEY=your_resend_api_key_here

# OPTIONAL: Custom sender email (must be from a verified domain)
# If not set, will use onboarding@resend.dev (only works for testing)
# RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com

# Setup Instructions:
# 1. Sign up for Resend account at https://resend.com
# 2. Get your API key from the dashboard
# 3. Copy this file to .env.local and add your API key
# 4. (Optional) Verify your domain in Resend to use custom sender email
# 5. Update RESEND_FROM_EMAIL if you have a verified domain

# Note: .env.local is gitignored and will not be committed to the repository
